Type: Package
Package: SpaDES.targets
Title: Orchestrate SpaDES Simulations with 'targets'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alex M", "Chubaty", , "achubaty@for-cast.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7146-8135"))
  )
Description: Helpers to run 'SpaDES' simulations (simInitAndSpades) as stages of
    a 'targets' pipeline. Each stage runs in-process and returns the discrete
    components the next stage needs -- plain objects as ordinary targets and
    spatial ('terra') objects as 'format = "file"' targets -- so whole simList
    objects are never serialized. Also provides a hard options "firewall" that
    disables the known-destructive 'reproducible'/'SpaDES.core' behaviours, plus
    spatial file-target and provenance helpers.
